{
  "stem": "3475.2",
  "chunk_idx": 7,
  "model": "openai/gpt-oss-120b",
  "elapsed_s": 4.0,
  "sentences_input": [
    {
      "segment_idx": 18,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "Before I left-- you know, when we-- when we went to the ghetto-- it comes back to me now-- I did see my mother for a short time, you know.",
      "word_count": 30
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 18,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "And she gave me a gold coin that she saved, a $20 gold coin.",
      "word_count": 14
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 18,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 3,
      "text": "So I had it with me.",
      "word_count": 6
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 18,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 4,
      "text": "But when I went to the Majdanek, there was nothing to do with the gold coin, you know.",
      "word_count": 18
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 18,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 5,
      "text": "So I had a relative there, an older-- I was a kid, you know.",
      "word_count": 14
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 18,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 6,
      "text": "I had an older relative.",
      "word_count": 5
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 18,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 7,
      "text": "And he says, if you give me the gold coin, I will see that you have food.",
      "word_count": 17
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 18,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 8,
      "text": "I'll buy it.",
      "word_count": 3
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 19,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "So I gave him the gold coin.",
      "word_count": 7
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 19,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "But I never saw anything.",
      "word_count": 5
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 19,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "[LAUGHS] He just took it, you know.",
      "word_count": 7
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 19,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 3,
      "text": "So people were mostly-- well, this particular person, you know, was-- now that I look-- but even before the war, a con man, you know.",
      "word_count": 25
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 19,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 4,
      "text": "So I entrusted him because I knew him, you know.",
      "word_count": 10
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 19,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 5,
      "text": "And I never saw-- I don't want to mention the name because his relatives are still alive.",
      "word_count": 17
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 19,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 6,
      "text": "So no use bringing it up.",
      "word_count": 6
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 19,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 7,
      "text": "So that's what stands out.",
      "word_count": 5
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 20,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "But also what steps up in my mind is, like, when they drove us to work, watching the guards torturing the prisoners.",
      "word_count": 22
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 20,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "You know, like lay-- like I said, laying a 2' by 4' across the neck, and, and a rock on the throat, you know.",
      "word_count": 24
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 20,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "But this, this is probably what stands out in my own mind-- and always trying to be someplace else where the guard was-- you know, trying to avoid, yeah.",
      "word_count": 29
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 20,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 3,
      "text": "And the speeches that they gave us, the Polish-- the, the, the, the guards-- the Polish guards, that, that we'll never survive this camp.",
      "word_count": 24
    }
  ],
